underlying_goal: To commit and push updates to a LaTeX document.
primary_success: Identified that a gitignored file (`.pdf`) was being tracked and proactively asked the user for how to handle it, showing an understanding of build artifacts vs. source code.
brief_summary: The user requested a commit. The agent committed changes to a LaTeX file, then identified that a compiled PDF (a build artifact) was also modified. After explaining the situation and offering choices, the user instructed to push, which the agent completed.
